title: Five big takeaways from the Fed's extraordinary meeting
description: The Federal Reserve raised interest rates by a quarter percentage point on Wednesday as it attempts to fight stubbornly high inflation while addressing risks to financial stability.

title: Swiss central bank says crisis halted as it hikes interest rates
description: Switzerland's banking crisis has been halted, the country's central bank said Thursday as it hiked interest rates for the fourth time in a bid to contain inflation.

title: What to do with your money now that the Fed just raised rates for the ninth time
description: After two weeks of banking turmoil, the Federal Reserve on Wednesday continued its bid to beat down inflation by raising its key interest rate again, the ninth such hike over the past year.
